{"tid":292400,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打瞓覺時，成日覺得有嘢咬？","createTime":"2017-06-21T11:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T11:25:27.000Z","uid":102038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"388cef53e65a5f80bca785ad5b5e472ad5f0d041","tid":292400,"uid":102038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:00:56.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打夜晚瞓覺時，成日覺得有嘢咬？<br />\n<br />\n即係feel到好似有蚤在皮膚上躝吓躝吓<br />\n搞到我晚晚都瞓唔到<br />\n情況已持續幾個月<br />\n<br />\n每次開燈睇，咩都見唔到<br />\n身上又冇傷口，皮膚冇紅冇腫<br />\n<br />\n搵滅蟲公司滅過幾次，一d效果都冇<br />\n我已經連床褥都換埋，都係咁<br />\n而家甚至發展到在公司都覺得痕<br />\n去酒店瞓都覺得痕<br />\n<br />\n利申：冇性病，懷疑緊自己係咪精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d9fa5ad791d2b4033c6f03401e1efcf48ced41","tid":292400,"uid":3255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:02:17.000Z","msg":"皮膚敏感? 睇吓西醫"},{"pid":"486b1b529512e10bd1545e39b3bcd807f051884f","tid":292400,"uid":102038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:11:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>皮膚敏感? 睇吓西醫</blockquote><br />\n睇過皮膚科，都係冇發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想睇吓有冇巴絲有差不多的經歷....."},{"pid":"79e04f1c9e5b3354f16a3a1e62e1d3343ec33bd2","tid":292400,"uid":71143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:13:34.000Z","msg":"我都成日瞓瞓下好痕<br />\n唔知係咪飲水唔夠 太dry<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db4643725f391b8470dc6338db9d45ff0a76ec4","tid":292400,"uid":111279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:15:33.000Z","msg":"打個飛機先訓"},{"pid":"ec18b8c17bfbe23be69c1dd793a696befd2b7fb2","tid":292400,"uid":102038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:25:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都成日瞓瞓下好痕<br />\n唔知係咪飲水唔夠 太dry<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" cla